text: Within minutes of President Donald Trump’s formal nomination of Amy Coney Barrett to sit on the Supreme Court, the GOP majority made clear that it essentially already has the votes to confirm her https://t.co/XKXtRzjhL3

text: Amy Coney Barrett’s ascent to the Supreme Court is not yet assured — but it could have earth-shaking consequences for American law https://t.co/PGa2WvkrI7

text:
